<div class="title">Pleasant Despite Stressful Circumstances</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=P&Exact=1">P</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; P. "Pleasant Despite Stressful Circumstances: An Experience with 2C-B (exp67684)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 5, 2008. erowid.org/exp/67684</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
